Difffold wraps wide diffs

When the FreeBSD docs repository switched to ASCIIDoc, we ended up with
long lines in the files.  This made it easier to track changes in
some ways, because we didn't have to wrap lines... but it made it harder
to read diffs, because we didn't wrap lines!

This utility wraps any diff to 80 characters wide, but zips the lines
together, for example:

